<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Erfurt</head><p>Der Rat teilt mit, dass die Jüdin Jutta Mayr, Bürgerin zu Nürnberg, wegen ihres Sohns Joel nichts unternehmen will.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_470" id="234v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_470_r2l24">Erfürt </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_470_r2l25"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>ewnde</ex></expan> / Als Jr vns <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von Juten Judin <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> <expan>B<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>er</ex>in</expan> / vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_470_r2l26">Jöhel 
<del rend="strikethrough">Jm </del> ewrs Judens irs Suns <expan>vveg<ex>en</ex></expan> / . Davon <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir mit </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_470_r2l27"><expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> Jüdin reden laſſen / vnd die ſprichet / Sie wölle die </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_470_r2l28">ſache als gen <expan>de<ex>m</ex>ſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> Jrem Sun yecʒunden 
<del rend="strikethrough"> beſtel </del> beſteen laſſen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_470_r2l29">vnd <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> cʒü der cʒeit nicht handeln / wo wir etc </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_470" id="234v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Erfürt </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde,</ex></expan> als ir uns
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von Juten, judin,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>b<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>er</ex>in,</expan> und Jöhel, ewrs judens, irs suns,
                                <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, davon <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        wir mit <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan> jüdin reden lassen und die sprichet, sie
                        wölle die sache als gen <expan>de<ex>m</ex>selb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> irem sun
                        yeczunden besteen lassen und <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> czü der czeit nicht
                        handeln. Wo wir etc. </ab>
</div>
</div></body>
